stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION

    RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION --> RAW_STANDING: posture_z >= standing_threshold
    RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION --> RAW_SITTING: posture_z >= sitting_threshold\nAND posture_z < standing_threshold
    RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION --> RAW_LYING: posture_z < sitting_threshold

    RAW_STANDING --> BUFFER_GATE
    RAW_SITTING --> BUFFER_GATE
    RAW_LYING --> BUFFER_GATE

    BUFFER_GATE --> STABLE_UNKNOWN: init (before first 8-frame consensus)
    BUFFER_GATE --> STABLE_STANDING: len(posture_buf)==POSTURE_CONFIRM\nAND all entries == STANDING
    BUFFER_GATE --> STABLE_SITTING: len(posture_buf)==POSTURE_CONFIRM\nAND all entries == SITTING
    BUFFER_GATE --> STABLE_LYING: len(posture_buf)==POSTURE_CONFIRM\nAND all entries == LYING_DOWN

    STABLE_UNKNOWN --> RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION: next frame
    STABLE_STANDING --> RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION: next frame
    STABLE_SITTING --> RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION: next frame
    STABLE_LYING --> RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION: next frame

    note right of RAW_POSTURE_ESTIMATION
      Inputs:
      - tracked (x,y,z)
      - valid candidates
      Derived proxy:
      posture_z = max(z of candidates within posture_z_neighborhood_m) + posture_z_bias
      fallback: tracked z when no nearby candidates
    end note

    note right of RAW_STANDING
      Confidence:
      conf = min(100, 60 + (posture_z - standing_threshold) * 80)
    end note

    note right of RAW_SITTING
      Confidence:
      conf = 70
    end note

    note right of RAW_LYING
      Confidence:
      conf = min(100, 75 + (sitting_threshold - posture_z) * 80)
    end note

    note right of BUFFER_GATE
      Gating / hysteresis:
      POSTURE_CONFIRM = 8 frames (default)
      stable_posture updates only when 8 consecutive raw labels agree.
      Output posture each frame is stable_posture, not raw_posture.
    end note
